Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:12.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照假名的顺序决定座位，相川是「あ」开头坐最前，櫟井是「い」开头排第二。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是相川  所以每次总是坐在最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边坐的是「い」…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栎井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有点儿不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话那本很厚的入学指南里有详细地写着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在暑假里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一直很在意的栎井同学她们的关系能够变得更好一些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野野原同学的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发给我这个  我要怎么回复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:03:00.07,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,120)\fad(500,500)}班长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天野野原同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  刚才那个是谁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认识吗  体育课的时候还一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太擅长记住别人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的  话说这是有脸大声讲出来的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柚子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你带了个眼镜来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在学校几乎不戴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想被人看出我很聪明的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来确实挺聪明的  只不过想法上有点蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听我说听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从今天早上开始状态就特别的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多好呢  有多好的状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是「不错哟」「真好啊」这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看出你姿势不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说状态好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是干劲？  感觉干劲十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么好不容易有这机会  就要好好为他人服务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这一手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这一手吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么停顿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子  拿出点干劲来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？拿出点？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲光线？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是从指头里出来的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  下次一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有也去下那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.51,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉提心吊胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才尽情地沐浴了干劲光线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子  光线是什么系的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲…全部都放出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有的干劲  在上课前就用光了要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说些让我有干劲的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤…烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲子丼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河豚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.81,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么全都是食物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥鹅肝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北极贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请问怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮您拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「妈妈」一词已经深入人心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去社团活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  昨晚我玩拼图时想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会看到一块这种形状的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课上你居然画这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好喜欢那种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是反过来又感觉很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前拼过一个大海的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那拼图是什么图案的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟人系列
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱因斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的瞬间感觉IQ会提升20厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的错觉  话说厘米是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小相相  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这感觉是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在书店搞好关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去社团活动？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小相相回见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近被其他同学也称呼为妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妈妈完全表现出了妈妈的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全表现吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的话那确实也只能没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没办法的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妈妈来当我们的妈妈就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子没有妈妈的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  妈妈…一次  一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以好好喊你一声妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个…老师我可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这演的是哪一出？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  就一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿妈妈嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师已经不知道什么是正确答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有什么正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  我只是想忽悠你一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这品性真是太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是青春期孩子们特有的对大人的那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  真是复杂呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生随着年龄的成长总会来的那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况不能用这种说法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期哦  很麻烦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被一个不经意的意外伤害到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如玻璃一般哦  很容易碎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纤细柔弱到爆的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期还真是让人劳神啊  真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  她们都是口胡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母都还健在  完全不是什么玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是铁板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用青春期来做挡箭牌  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事的  老师就是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这般劣性的我以后也还可以称呼您为妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿妈妈  Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈吗  我还很年轻的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是松本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈吗  感觉这样看大家都变得很可爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老找老师麻烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天的主题就定为鲸鱼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是鲸鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  我对妈妈的爱就如同鲸鱼一般大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对小唯的爱也像鲸鱼一样大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然到现在才说　我们老这样随意地决定主题真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？网上说座头鲸的歌声恐怕是动物界中最复杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄性会在交配期歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鲸鱼是为了攻陷女朋友而唱那么难度拔群的歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉形象改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌吗  好羞人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  长须鲸的心脏居然有600公斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最粗的血管直径有20cm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好粗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个很羞人的鲸鱼是座头鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？长须先生不唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長須鯨（ながすくじら）和長瀬（ながせ）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫得像长濑先生似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面说睡觉的时候也在游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脑和右脑交替休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:13:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么迷迷糊糊的长须鲸  时而像理科生时而充满艺术细胞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有点困了  属于哪种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  52x31x86=？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微费点时间可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这仅仅是犯迷糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:30.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1160,140)}佐藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说利用超声波来交流信息的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:30.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,200)}史密斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果血缘相差太远的话交流起来是很困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这样说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的亲戚说我好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的亲戚说我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下DNA和河马是近亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？河马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鲸鱼是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再顺便说下它们有四个胃 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼是什么星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地球的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}鲸鱼总结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}不管好坏总之很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}本体是啥不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}总觉得没法讨厌它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  鲸鱼  到头来也没怎么弄明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼的种种都好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不像是总结的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}鲸鱼总结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}有点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…感觉好困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电池用完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  没劲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小说太好看了  一口气看完直接早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史小说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋小唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一节是英语来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什么程度「どのくらい」和「Don't cry」发音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不是Don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯因为太困变成笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  不管发生了什么我们都一直在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我是妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好复杂的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要这样哦  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  快醒醒  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点  快起来  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.35,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈我都准备好了膝枕  快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵  给吾退下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有两个妈妈了  再加上笨蛋唯武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽点太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你俩赶紧滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,660)\fs32}Don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离午休还有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  英语？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两节课哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才要说「我没哭」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟蹋了睡意中的小唯使出浑身解数想出来的段子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那个打算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  对不起  我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的你们俩别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再轻松欢乐一些  什么都不想地聊聊天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士超人战士的外号一定是武士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子同学总是好突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会想吃羊栖菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pheromone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)\fs30}动物激素
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单词？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是什么都没在想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:37.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}法国的启蒙思想家。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟…孟…孟德斯鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pheromone「フェロモン」应该用「n」来接，但在词语接龙里是犯规的。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我用「孟」来接了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有时会完全钻牛角尖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  虽然说看不到摸不着  事实上是有空气存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你还是用脑子想想再说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  再有一节课就午休了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像克服了睡眠的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  让我袭胸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在这里  进屋再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栎井同学  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是相川同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…接着就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栎井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上开始好像就不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她真熬不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一节课的老师是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神崎老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去和她说声  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把睡相拍下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！我也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔弱的小唯好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也来一张  我拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍…拍下来可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来拍吧来拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是别人发而是自己拍下来的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有朋友的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是偷拍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去厕所的时间好长  便秘吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才去把栎井同学扶到保健室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副高兴的样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得绝症了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘？  柚子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人在学校  不要啊  好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课已经都上完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  我帮你把包拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能起得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  还困吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再睡一会儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小唯  把你内裤脱了对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
